with mock.patch.object(app, 'openFile', return_value=('config', 'test', 'cfg')
    ):
    with mock.patch.object(app.app, 'loadConfig', return_value=False):

                        assert suc
                    assert ['Profile              [test] cannot no be loaded',
                        2] == blocker.args
